author: Microsoft
description:
EY’s Global Consulting AI Leader Dan Diasio shares a powerful insight: AI can raise the floor, but not the ceiling. So how do we unlock its full potential? It’s not just AI—it’s AI and something: creativity, critical thinking, systems thinking, and deep domain expertise. Discover why context matters and what it takes to truly elevate outcomes in the age of AI.
